## üìù Notes

* To install additional Python packages:

  ```bash
  pip install <package>
  pip freeze > requirements.txt
  ```

* To suppress pipenv verbosity in environments where pipenv is used:

  ```bash
  export PIPENV_VERBOSITY=-1
  ```

